<br>
My first serious monk is now 18, (been practising ID like crazy, lol).<br>
<br>
My question is, is it better to fight multiple yellows in a row, or single reds (not too far above yellow).<br>
<br>
E.G. goblin warriors in loio are red, take a long time to kill, and still getting 1 blue (more or less) per kill. <br>
<br>
