<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#778899><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/bmonklybusiness43508.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=xen>Xen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Master</span><br>  Posts: 529<br> <font color=#8b1a1a>(7/3/02 9:27:04 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fmonklybusiness43508frm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1663.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: PLing with a cleric ... Red vs yellow/black/blue..</span><hr size=1> If you were PLing with a Druid (damage shields) I'd say kill as many reds as you can. But with a Cleric you're better off probably sticking to blues and yellows.<br>
<br>
