<br>
You are asking if you should single kill reds (with a recovery) or chain kill everything else (no recovery needed for ANY others).<br>
<br>
This to me sounds like you do not need any recovery after killing a yellow. IF this is true, I'm pretty sure that the chain killing method would benefit you the most.<br>
